sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer (WSL)
    participant Git as GitHub
    participant Agent as build-agent.js
    participant SP as SharePoint
    participant Watcher as deploy-watcher (Windows Service)
    participant IIS as IIS / App Pool

    Dev->>Git: 1. git push
    activate Agent
    Note over Dev,Agent: 2. pre-push hook dispara build-agent.js

    Agent->>Agent: 3. Lee deploy.config.yml
    Agent->>Agent: 4. git diff HEAD~1..HEAD<br/>detecta cambios en frontend/ o backend/

    alt Frontend cambió
        Agent->>Agent: 5. npm run build
        Agent->>Agent: 6. ZIP + SHA-256
        Agent->>SP: 7. Sube build ZIP
        Agent->>SP: 8. Actualiza manifest.json<br/>latest = nueva versión
    else Sin cambios relevantes
        Agent->>Agent: 5. skipping
    end
    deactivate Agent

    Git-->>Dev: 9. push completado

    loop Cada 30s
        Watcher->>SP: 10. GET manifest.json
        SP-->>Watcher: 11. { latest, builds[] }

        alt Nueva versión detectada
            Watcher->>SP: 12. Descarga ZIP
            Watcher->>Watcher: 13. Valida SHA-256

            alt deploy_mode: replace
                Watcher->>Watcher: 14a. Backup de inetpub_path
                Watcher->>IIS: 15a. Limpia y extrae ZIP en inetpub_path
                IIS-->>Watcher: Archivos reemplazados
            else deploy_mode: junction
                Watcher->>Watcher: 14b. Extrae ZIP en releases/{version}
                Watcher->>IIS: 15b. Swap Directory Junction<br/>current → releases/{version}
            end

            opt App Pool configurado
                Watcher->>IIS: 16. appcmd recycle apppool
            end

            opt Health check configurado
                Watcher->>IIS: 17. GET health check URL
                alt OK (200)
                    Watcher->>Watcher: 18. Limpia backup / purga releases viejos
                    Note over Watcher: ✓ Deploy exitoso
                else Falla
                    Watcher->>IIS: 18. Rollback (restaura backup o junction anterior)
                    Note over Watcher: ✗ Rollback automático
                end
            end

            Watcher->>Watcher: 19. Guarda estado (versión deployada)
        end
    end
